  -lhs2tex-1.17.ebuild:
  Thanks to Vikraman Choudhury <vikraman@gentoo.org> for this fix: dev-
  haskell/lhs2tex: Fix man page install location

*lhs2tex-1.18.1 (25 Nov 2012)

